                     </persName>
                     
                  , no person being therein, between the hours of eleven and twelve in the forenoon of the <rs id="t17880402-2-cd7" type="crimeDate">13th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880402-2-off6 t17880402-2-cd7"></join> last, and feloniously stealing therein, two pounds weight of beef, value 6 d. a cloth waistcoat, value<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178804020004"></xptr>10 s. a handkerchief, value 4 s. a pair of stockings, value 3 s. half a guinea, value 10 s. 6 d. the property of 
